PORTLAND, Ore. -- Employee layoffs will begin Monday morning at Bullseye Glass after receiving a cease-and-desist order from Oregon Gov. Kate Brown, the Department of Environmental Equality and the Oregon Health Authority.

Jim Jones, Vice President of Bullseye Glass, announced the layoffs Friday. He tells KATU News that they could be laying off around 20 percent of the company's staff.
